Readme:
========
Project: AmazonOriontek

This repository contains project for the challenge for Oriontek using Selenium WebDriver with Python and Pycharm
==================================================================================

Setup Instructions
Python Setup
OS : Windows
Python version: 3.8.3
You can download the latest Python version from Python.org.

==================================================================================
For virtualization: pipenv.
To install pipenv, run pip install pipenv from the command line.

For Python editor: Pycharm 2020.2.3

WebDriver Setup
Browser: Chrome version 86.0.4240.75

Install the chromeDriver according to the Chrome version

==================================================================================
Create a folder for the project cloned from Github and Move the executables files into this folder.


Project Setup
Clone this repository https://github.com/Gferrarese/amazonOriontek.git.
Run cd project cloned to enter the project.

Run pipenv install to install the dependencies.
Run pipenv run python -m pytest to verify that the framework can run tests.

Run pipenv install pytest from within the project directory.

Install Python packages directly using pip.

Run tests directly using python -m pytest. <----